section.def:
Authority
                (監督) means the Gas Authority appointed under
                section 5;

Committee
                (委員會) means the Gas Safety Advisory Committee
            established by section 4(1);

container
                (儲存器) means a bulk tank, mini-tank or
            cylinder;

employee
                (僱員) means a person who works for another person
            under a contract of employment;

exercise
                (行使), in relation to a function, includes perform
            and discharge;

order
                (命令) means an order under section
                19(4);

panel
                (委員團) means the appeal board panel appointed
            under section 17(1);

personal
                injury
                (身體受傷) includes death;

pressure-regulator
                (調壓器) means a device which automatically controls
            the pressure of gas in a gas pipe downstream of the device;

road
                (道路) means a road within the meaning of the Road
            Traffic Ordinance (Cap. 374);

substance
                (物品) means a natural or artificial substance,
            whether in the form of a solid, liquid or vapour;

transport
                (運送), in relation to liquefied petroleum gas,
            means the conveyance of such gas by a gas vehicle;

vehicle
                (車輛) means a vehicle within the meaning of the
            Road Traffic Ordinance (Cap. 374);

paragraph.content:
the laying out, construction, alteration or repair of any road, footpath,
                    tunnel, airport runway, canal, reservoir, pipe-line, railway or
                    tramway;

provide for records and other documents to be kept and maintained by
                    registered persons, owners of gas installations referred to in paragraph
                        (a)(iv) and owners of gas vehicles;

provide for references in the regulations to any specified document to
                    operate as a reference to such document as revised or re-issued from time to
                    time;

subparagraph.content:
decommission the installation until such time, if
                                                any, as the repairs or alterations are
                                                effected;

subsection.content:
The protection conferred on public officers by subsection (1) in respect of any
                act or omission shall not in any way affect any liability of the Government in tort
                for that act or omission. (Amended 61 of 2000 s. 3)
